# 🌐 prykhodd.com — My Personal Portfolio 🚀  

Welcome to my portfolio repository! This is where I showcase my work, projects, and experiments in **web development, AI, and software engineering**. Built with **Hugo**, deployed via **GitHub Pages**, and powered by **Cloudflare**.  

🌍 **Live site**: [https://prykhodd.com](https://prykhodd.com)  

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack  
- ⚡ **Hugo** – Fast static site generation  
- 🎨 **Custom CSS** – For a sleek design  
- ☁️ **GitHub Pages** – Deployment  
- 🔒 **Cloudflare** – Domain & security  

---

## 📂 Project Structure

- 📁 layouts/ → Hugo templates (base layout, pages, etc.) 
- 📁 static/ → Static assets (CSS, images, icons, etc.) 
- 📁 content/ → Page content (work, about, etc.) 
- 📄 config.toml → Hugo site configuration 
- 📄 .github/workflows → GitHub Actions for deployment


---

## 🚀 Running Locally

Clone the repo and run Hugo locally:  
```sh
git clone https://github.com/demianprykhodko/portfolio.git 
cd portfolio  
hugo server --disableFastRender  
```

Then visit http://localhost:1313 in your browser

